commands.name: az monitor app-insights workbook revision list
commands.summary: List the revisions for the workbook.
commands.syntax:
az monitor app-insights workbook revision list --resource-group
                                               --resource-name
                                               [--max-items]
                                               [--next-token]
examples: az monitor app-insights workbook revision list -g rg --resource-name name

commands.name: az monitor app-insights workbook revision show
commands.syntax:
az monitor app-insights workbook revision show [--ids]
                                               [--name]
                                               [--resource-group]
                                               [--resource-name]
                                               [--subscription]
examples: az monitor app-insights workbook revision list -g rg --resource-name name --revision-id id
